---
title: Mozzarella Pesto Chicken with Roasted Carrots and Lemony Rice
description: Cheesy chicken sounded pretty tough to top, but our chefs were up to the challenge. They went and made it 25x (a scientific number) more delicious by spreading a layer of bright, herby pesto beneath melty mozzarella. And while chicken is the main event here, the sides are excellent accompanying acts. We’re serving up crispy-edged roasted carrots and buttery, lemony rice for a sweet-and-savory sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/melty-mozzarella-pesto-chicken-fb4b2448.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/melty-mozzarella-pesto-chicken-5d35ceb1a641a5000f49d8dc-5028dfba.pdf
